<eesti>&Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Takeover Bid </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise kohustus </eesti>
<inglise>Obligation to make takeover bid </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumine k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on avalik pakkumine b&ouml;rsil noteeritud aktsiaemitendi (edaspidi sihtemitent) aktsion&auml;ridele (edaspidi sihtisikud) aktsiate omandamiseks raha v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite eest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, a takeover bid is a public tender for the acquisition of shares for money or securities to the shareholders (hereinafter target persons) of the issuer of shares quoted on the exchange (hereinafter target issuer). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Otseselt v&otilde;i koos koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutsevate isikutega sihtemitendi &uuml;le valitseva m&otilde;ju saanud isik on kohustatud v&auml;hemalt 10 p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates valitseva m&otilde;ju saamise p&auml;evast, tegema v&auml;hemalt 28 p&auml;eva kestva &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise sihtemitendi k&otilde;igi aktsiate suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A person who has gained dominant influence over the target issuer directly or together with persons acting in concert is required to make a takeover bid for all shares of the target issuer with a duration of at least twenty-eight days within at least ten days after the date of gaining dominant influence. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Valitsev m&otilde;ju on olukord, kus sihtemitent on v&otilde;i muutub tehingu t&auml;itmisel kontrollitavaks &auml;ri&uuml;hinguks krediidiasutuste seaduse (RT I 1999, 23, 349) &sect; 10 l&otilde;ike 2 punktide 1-3 t&auml;henduses, kusjuures h&auml;&auml;le&otilde;iguse arvestamisel l&auml;htutakse krediidiasutuste seaduse &sect; 10 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatust. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Dominant influence is a situation where the target issuer is or upon performance of a transaction becomes a controlled company within the meaning of clauses 10 (2) 1) -3) of the Credit Institutions Act (RT I 1999, 23, 349), whereas the calculation of voting rights shall be based on subsection 10 (1) of the Credit Institutions Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutsevad isikud on kontrollitav &auml;ri&uuml;hing, seda &auml;ri&uuml;hingut kontrolliv isik ja teised selle isiku poolt kontrollitavad &auml;ri&uuml;hingud (edaspidi seotud isikud), samuti isikud, kes tegutsevad koos &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumist tegeva isiku (edaspidi pakkuja) v&otilde;i sihtemitendiga suulise v&otilde;i kirjaliku kokkuleppe alusel eesm&auml;rgiga saavutada, s&auml;ilitada v&otilde;i suurendada valitsevat m&otilde;ju sihtemitendi &uuml;le v&otilde;i eesm&auml;rgiga nurjata &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumine. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Persons acting in concert are a controlled company, a person controlling this company and other companies controlled by this person (hereinafter connected persons), also persons who act together with the person making the takeover bid (hereinafter tenderer) or the target issuer on the basis of an oral or written agreement in order to gain, maintain or increase dominant control over the target issuer or in order to frustrate the takeover bid. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24 (2). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24 (2). </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumisega seotud isikute kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Obligations of persons connected with takeover bid </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Pakkuja peab samaliigiliste aktsiate omanikke kohtlema v&otilde;rdselt. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A tenderer shall treat all holders of shares of the same class equally. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Pakkuja ja sihtemitent peavad andma sihtisikutele &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise kaalumiseks olulist, &otilde;iget, t&auml;pset, t&auml;ielikku ja &uuml;hesugust teavet. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A tenderer and target issuer shall provide the target persons with significant, correct, accurate, complete and identical information for considering a takeover bid. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sihtemitendi tegevjuhtkonna, juhatuse ja n&otilde;ukogu liikmed peavad &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise korral l&auml;htuma sihtemitendi huvidest ning ei tohi takistada sihtisikutel &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise kaalumist. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the case of a takeover bid, members of the management, management board and supervisory board of the target issuer shall be guided by the interests of the target issuer and shall not hinder the consideration of the takeover bid by target persons. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Pakkuja, sihtemitent ja nendega koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutsevad isikud on kohustatud &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise t&auml;htajal hoiduma tegudest, mis p&otilde;hjustavad sihtemitendi aktsiate ebaharilikku hinnak&otilde;ikumist. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Tenderers, target issuers and persons acting in concert with them are required to refrain from activities which cause the unusual price fluctuation of shares of the target issuer during the term of a takeover bid. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Pakkuja, juriidilisest isikust pakkuja tegevjuhtkonna, juhatuse, n&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;i neid asendava organi liikmed, sihtemitent, selle sihtemitendi tegevjuhtkonna, juhatuse ja n&otilde;ukogu liikmed, eelnimetatutega koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutsevad isikud ja sihtemitendi aktsion&auml;rid on kohustatud n&otilde;uetekohaselt t&auml;itma selle b&ouml;rsi reglemendi &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumist reguleerivaid s&auml;tteid, kus sihtemitendi aktsiad on noteeritud. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A tenderer, members of the management, management board or supervisory board or the body substituting the management of a tenderer who is a legal person, a target issuer, members of the management, management board or supervisory board of the target issuer, persons acting in concert with the above-mentioned persons and shareholders of the target issuer are required to comply with the provisions which regulate a takeover bid and are contained in the rules of the exchange which quotes the shares of the target issuer as required. </inglise>
<eesti>Pakkuja ja b&ouml;rs s&otilde;lmivad lepingu vastava sihtemitendi suhtes &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise l&auml;biviimiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>The tenderer and the exchange shall enter into a contract for conducting a takeover bid in respect of the corresponding target issuer. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Pakkujal ja temaga koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutseval isikul ei ole &otilde;igust teha sama sihtemitendi suhtes uut &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumist &uuml;he aasta jooksul &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) Tenderers and persons acting in concert with them do not have the right to make a new takeover bid in respect of the same target issuer within one year as of the expiry of the term of the takeover bid. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24 (3). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24 (3). </inglise>
<eesti>B&ouml;rsi kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Obligations of exchange </inglise>
<eesti>B&ouml;rs on k&auml;esolevas seaduses toodud p&otilde;him&otilde;tetest l&auml;htudes kohustatud k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-de 24 (1) ja 24 (2) rakendamiseks oma reglemendis t&auml;iendavalt s&auml;testama allj&auml;rgnevad kohustusliku ja vabatahtliku &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumisega seotud asjaolud (edaspidi &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglid): </eesti>
<inglise>Based on the principles set out in this Act, the exchange is required to additionally provide the following facts related to mandatory and voluntary takeover bids (hereinafter rules for takeover bid) in the rules thereof in order to implement &sect;&sect; 24 (1) and 24 (2) of this Act: </inglise>
<eesti>1) erakorralise ajutise asjaolu tunnused, mille puhul isikul on b&ouml;rsi n&otilde;usolekul &otilde;igus loobuda kohustusliku &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemisest; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the elements of extraordinary temporary circumstances in the case of which the person has the right to withdraw from making a mandatory takeover bid with the consent of the exchange; </inglise>
<eesti>2) ostuhinna m&auml;&auml;ramise ja tasumise kriteeriumid ning menetlus; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the criteria and procedure for determination and payment of the purchase price; </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise muutmine ja sellest taganemine, pakkumise maksimumt&auml;htaeg, tingimuslikkuse kriteeriumid; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the amendment of a takeover bid and withdrawal therefrom, the maximum term of the tender and the conditionality criteria; </inglise>
<eesti>4) &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise avalikustamisele eelnev b&ouml;rsi kontrollmenetluse kord ja selle t&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the procedure for control proceedings of the exchange before publication of a takeover bid, and the term thereof; </inglise>
<eesti>5) &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise avalikustamise ja teabe edastamise kriteeriumid ja menetlus; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the criteria and procedure for the publication of a takeover bid and dissemination of information; </inglise>
<eesti>6) &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise k&otilde;iki tingimusi kajastava dokumendi sisu- ja vormin&otilde;uded; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the requirements for the content and format of a document containing all conditions of a takeover bid; </inglise>
<eesti>7) &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tulemuste avalikustamise kriteeriumid ja menetlus; </eesti>
<inglise>7) the criteria and procedure for publication of the results of a takeover bid; </inglise>
<eesti>8) &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise esemeks olnud aktsiate jaotamine pakkujale; </eesti>
<inglise>8) the distribution of shares which are the object of a takeover bid to tenderers; </inglise>
<eesti>9) pakkuja kohustused tema poolt sihtemitendi aktsia omandamisel soodsamatel tingimustel, kui &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumises on ette n&auml;htud; </eesti>
<inglise>9) the obligations of the tenderer upon acquisition of the shares of the target issuer by him or her under more favourable terms than prescribed in a takeover bid; </inglise>
<eesti>10) sihtemitendi arvamuse sisu- ning vormin&otilde;uded &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise ja sellega seonduvate asjaolude kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>10) the requirements for the content and format of the opinion of the target issuer concerning a takeover bid and circumstances relating thereto; </inglise>
<eesti>11) sihtemitendi ebakohaste kaitsev&otilde;tete tunnused; </eesti>
<inglise>11) the nature of improper defensive measures taken by the target issuer; </inglise>
<eesti>12) v&otilde;istleva &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise puhul kehtivad s&auml;tted ja v&otilde;istleva pakkumise m&otilde;ju esialgsele pakkumisele; </eesti>
<inglise>12) the provisions which apply in the case of a competing takeover bid and the influence of a competing tender on the initial tender; </inglise>
<eesti>13) pakkuja ja b&ouml;rsi vahel s&otilde;lmitava lepingu olulised tingimused; </eesti>
<inglise>13) the terms of a contract entered into between a tenderer and the exchange; </inglise>
<eesti>14) b&ouml;rsi p&auml;devus &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise avalikustamisele eelneva ja muu &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumisega seoses teostatava kontrollmenetluse tegemisel. </eesti>
<inglise>14) the competence of the exchange upon conducting control proceedings before publication of a takeover bid or in connection with another takeover bid. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24 (4). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24 (4). </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglite koosk&otilde;lastamine ja avaldamine </eesti>
<inglise>Approval and publication of rules for takeover bid </inglise>
<eesti>(1) B&ouml;rs on kohustatud enne &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglite kehtestamist v&otilde;i muutmist esitama need koosk&otilde;lastamiseks v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Before establishment or amendment of the rules for a takeover bid, the exchange is required to submit the rules to the securities supervision authority for approval. </inglise>
<eesti>Selleks tuleb v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele esitada vastav avaldus, b&ouml;rsi reglemendi kehtiv tekst ja &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglite v&otilde;i nende muutmise projekt. </eesti>
<inglise>For this purpose, a corresponding application, the valid text of the rules of the exchange and the draft of the rules for the takeover bid or amendment thereof shall be submitted to the securities supervision authority. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve teeb otsuse &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglite koosk&otilde;lastamise v&otilde;i sellest keeldumise kohta 20 p&auml;eva jooksul k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud k&otilde;igi dokumentide saamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The securities supervision authority shall make a decision on approval of the rules for a takeover bid or refusal to approve within twenty days after receipt of all documents specified in subsection (1) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>Koosk&otilde;lastamisest keeldutakse, kui &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglid ei vasta &otilde;igusaktidele, on vastuolulised, eksitavad v&otilde;i puudulikud v&otilde;i kui nende rakendamine ei taga investorite huvide k&uuml;llaldast kaitset. </eesti>
<inglise>Approval shall be refused if the rules for the takeover bid are not in compliance with legislation, are contradicting, misleading or insufficient, or if application thereof does not ensure sufficient protection of the interests of investors. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) B&ouml;rs avaldab &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglid viivitamatult p&auml;rast nende koosk&otilde;lastamist ametlikus v&auml;ljaandes Ametlikud Teadaanded. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The exchange shall publish the rules for a takeover bid promptly after approval thereof in the official publication Ametlikud Teadaanded1. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>IV osa </eesti>
<inglise>Part IV </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru j&auml;relevalve </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision over Securities Market </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kontroll </eesti>
<inglise>Monitoring of securities market </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kontrollimise eesm&auml;rgiks on investorite huvide ja &otilde;iguste kaitse. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The objective of monitoring the securities market is to protect the interests and rights of investors. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalvet k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 2 nimetatud isikute (edaspidi v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru osalised) tegevuse &uuml;le v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul teostab v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The activities of persons specified in &sect; 2 of this Act (hereinafter securities market participants) in the securities market shall be supervised by the securities supervision authority. </inglise>
<eesti>(10.06.98 j&otilde;ust. 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979) </eesti>
<inglise>(10.06.98 entered into force 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvel on k&auml;esolevast seadusest tulenevate &uuml;lesannete t&auml;itmiseks &otilde;igus saada andmeid ja dokumente v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru osalistelt, riigi- ja kohaliku omavalitsuse asutustelt, Eesti Pangalt ning riigi andmekogude vastutavatelt ja volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejatelt, samuti Eesti V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite Keskregistri pidajalt, k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 23, &sect; 24 l&otilde;ikes 2, &sect; 24 (1) l&otilde;igetes 2 ja 4 nimetatud ning teistelt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru osalistega seotud isikutelt. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The securities supervision authority has the right to receive data and documents from securities market participants, state and local government agencies, the Bank of Estonia and chief processors and authorised processors of state databases, the registrar of the Estonian Central Register of Securities, persons specified in &sect; 23, subsection 24 (2) and subsections 24 (1) (2) and (4) of this Act and other persons connected with securities market participants for the performance of duties arising from this Act. </inglise>

<eesti>01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979; 18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(10.06.98 entered into force 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979; 18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise kontroll </eesti>
<inglise>Monitoring of takeover bid </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise vastavust seadusele ja b&ouml;rsi reglemendile kontrollib reglemendis s&auml;testatud korras b&ouml;rs, kes noteerib sihtemitendi aktsiaid. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The exchange which quotes the shares of the target issuer shall monitor compliance of a takeover bid with law and the rules of the exchange pursuant to the procedure provided for in the rules. </inglise>
<eesti>B&ouml;rs keelab seaduse v&otilde;i oma reglemendiga vastuolus oleva &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemise ja avalikustamise. </eesti>
<inglise>The exchange shall prohibit the making and publication of a takeover bid which is contrary to law or the rules of the exchange. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Seaduse v&otilde;i vastava b&ouml;rsi reglemendiga vastuolus olev, selles reglemendis s&auml;testatud viisil kontrollimata v&otilde;i avalikustamata &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumine ning sellega seoses tehtud tehingud on t&uuml;hised. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A takeover bid which is contrary to law or the rules of the corresponding exchange, or is not monitored or published in a manner provided for in these rules, and transactions concluded in connection therewith are void. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Isiku poolt k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 24 (1) l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatu rikkumisel, kui isikule ei olnud antud n&otilde;usolekut loobuda kohustusliku &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemisest vastavalt &sect; 24 (3) punktis 1 s&auml;testatule, ei saa isik kuni rikkumise l&otilde;ppemiseni teostada h&auml;&auml;le&otilde;igusi sihtemitendis ning neid h&auml;&auml;li ei arvata sihtemitendi &uuml;ldkoosoleku kvoorumisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon violation of the provisions of subsection 24 (1) (2) of this Act by a person if the person is not granted consent to withdraw from making a mandatory takeover bid pursuant to the provisions of clause 24 (3) (1), the person cannot exercise a voting right in the target issuer until termination of the violation and these votes are not included in the quorum of the general meeting of the target issuer. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui h&auml;&auml;led arvati sihtemitendi &uuml;ldkoosoleku kvoorumisse, v&otilde;ib kohus sihtemitendi, selle n&otilde;ukogu liikme v&otilde;i aktsion&auml;ri avalduse alusel tunnistada sihtemitendi vastava &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse kehtetuks, kui avaldus on esitatud kolme kuu jooksul sihtemitendi &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>If votes were included in the quorum of the general meeting of the target issuer, a court may declare the resolution of the corresponding general meeting of the target issuer invalid on the basis of an application of the target issuer, a member of the supervisory board, or a shareholder thereof if the application is submitted within three months after adoption of the resolution of the general meeting of the target issuer. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 26. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 26. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve teostamine ja andmete salastatus </eesti>
<inglise>Conduct of supervision and confidentiality of data </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve juhi poolt j&auml;relevalvemenetlust teostama volitatud ametnikul (edaspidi kontrollija) on &otilde;igus kontrollida v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru osalise k&otilde;iki v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitehinguid, nendega seotud panga- ja muid arveid ning dokumente niiv&otilde;rd, kuiv&otilde;rd see on vajalik j&auml;relevalve teostamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An official authorised by a head of the securities supervision authority to conduct supervision proceedings (hereinafter inspector) has the right to inspect all securities transactions of securities market participants, and bank accounts, other accounts and documents related to securities transactions, in so far as this is necessary for the conduct of supervision. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontrollijal on seejuures &otilde;igus n&otilde;uda ka andmeid ja dokumente, mis on pangasaladuseks krediidiasutuste seaduse t&auml;henduses, samuti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru osalise k&auml;sutuses olevaid teise osalise kohta k&auml;ivaid andmeid ja dokumente. </eesti>
<inglise>The inspector has the right to require data and documents which are deemed to be information subject to banking secrecy within the meaning of the Credit Institutions Act, and data and documents at the disposal of a securities market participant relating to another participant. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontrollijal on &otilde;igus teha k&otilde;igist kontrollitavatest dokumentidest v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid, &auml;rakirju ja koopiaid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Inspectors have the right to make extracts from and copies of all inspected documents. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontrollija on kohustatud koostama kontrollimise kohta akti, mis esitatakse tutvumiseks v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru osalisele v&otilde;i tema poolt volitatud isikule, kes annab aktiga tutvumise kohta allkirja. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An inspector is required to prepare a report concerning an inspection which shall be submitted for review to the securities market participant or a person authorised thereby who shall sign the report to confirm the review thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) J&auml;relevalvetegevuse k&auml;igus saadud avalikustamata andmed on salajased ega kuulu avaldamisele ilma isiku, kelle k&auml;est need on saadud, ja isiku, kelle &auml;risaladuseks need on, n&otilde;usolekuta. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Undisclosed data received in the course of supervision activities are confidential and not subject to disclosure without the consent of the person from whom the data are received and the person whose business secret such data are. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve teenistuja v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;taja, samuti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve volitusel tegutsenud audiitorid, eksperdid ja teised isikud on kohustatud j&auml;relevalvetegevuse k&auml;igus saadud teavet pidama saladuses t&auml;htajatult. </eesti>
<inglise>Public servants and employees of the securities supervision authority and auditors, experts and other persons acting upon authorisation of the securities supervision authority are required to maintain the confidentiality of information received in the course of supervision activities for an unspecified term. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;ue ei laiene andmetele, mille avaldamine on seaduse alusel kohustuslik. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The requirement provided for in subsection (4) of this section does not extend to data which is subject to disclosure pursuant to law. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kuriteo v&otilde;i haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise t&otilde;kestamise, kurjategija v&otilde;i &otilde;iguserikkuja tabamise v&otilde;i kriminaal- v&otilde;i haldusmenetluses t&otilde;e v&auml;ljaselgitamise huvides v&otilde;ib v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve anda isiku, kelle k&auml;est need on saadud, v&otilde;i isiku, kelle &auml;risaladuseks need on, n&otilde;usoleku ja teadmiseta informatsiooni kohtule v&otilde;i p&auml;devale riigiasutusele kriminaal- v&otilde;i haldusmenetluses oleva asja uurimiseks, menetlemiseks ja arutamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) In the interests of preventing a criminal or administrative offence, of apprehending a criminal offender or administrative offender, or ascertaining the truth in a criminal or administrative proceeding, the securities supervision authority may provide information to a court or a competent state agency without the consent or knowledge of the person from whom the data is received or the person whose business secret such data are, for the investigation, hearing and consideration of a matter subject to criminal or administrative proceeding. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud andmeid v&otilde;ib avaldada Eesti Pangale ja Kindlustusinspektsioonile ning teiste riikide finantsj&auml;relevalve asutustele nendega s&otilde;lmitud koost&ouml;&ouml;kokkulepete alusel tingimusel, et edastatud informatsiooni kasutatakse ainult j&auml;relevalve eesm&auml;rkidel ning nimetatud asutuste teenistujatele ja t&ouml;&ouml;tajatele laieneb saladuse pidamise kohustus. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The data specified in subsection (4) of this section may be disclosed to the Bank of Estonia and the Insurance Supervisory Authority, and to the financial supervision authorities of other countries on the basis of co-operation agreements entered into therewith, on the condition that the information provided shall be used only for supervision purposes and the duty to maintain confidentiality extends to the public servants and employees of such authorities. </inglise>
<eesti>(10.06.98 j&otilde;ust. 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979) </eesti>
<inglise>(10.06.98 entered into force 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979) </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Krediidiasutused on kohustatud avaldama v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele tema juhi kirjalikul j&auml;relep&auml;rimisel j&auml;relevalve teostamiseks andmeid, mida krediidiasutuste seaduse &sect; 88 l&otilde;ike 1 kohaselt k&auml;sitatakse pangasaladusena. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) Credit institutions are required to disclose information which is deemed to be information subject to banking secrecy pursuant to subsection 88 (1) of the Credit Institutions Act to the securities supervision authority upon a written inquiry of the head thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relep&auml;rimisele kohaldatakse krediidiasutuste seaduse &sect; 88 l&otilde;igetes 6 ja 7 s&auml;testatut. </eesti>
<inglise>The provisions of subsections 88 (6) and (7) of the Credit Institutions Act apply to inquiries. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 27. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 27. </inglise>
<eesti>Aruannete ja andmete esitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Submission of reports and information </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselised osalised on kohustatud esitama v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele aruandeid ja andmeid vastavalt rahandusministri kehtestatud korrale. </eesti>
<inglise>Professional securities market participants are required to submit reports and data to the securities supervision authority pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 28. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 28. </inglise>
<eesti>Vaidluste lahendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Resolution of disputes </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutseliste osaliste ja emitentide ning v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve vahelised vaidlused lahendatakse &otilde;igusaktides kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>Disputes between professional securities market participants, issuers and the securities supervision authority shall be resolved pursuant to the procedure established by legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 29. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 29. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve ettekirjutus v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul osalejale </eesti>
<inglise>Precepts of securities supervision authority to securities market participants </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolevast seadusest ja sellest tulenevatest &otilde;igusaktidest l&auml;htudes v&otilde;ib v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve teha v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul osalejale t&auml;itmiseks kohustusliku ettekirjutuse &otilde;iguserikkumise l&otilde;petamiseks v&otilde;i teatud toimingute sooritamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Based on this Act and legislation arising therefrom, the securities supervision authority may issue mandatory precepts to securities market participants for termination of a violation of law or for performance of specific acts. </inglise>
<eesti>(1 (1)) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvel on &otilde;igus teha Eesti V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite Keskregistri pidajale viivitamatuks t&auml;itmiseks kohustuslik ettekirjutus blokeerida t&auml;htajaliselt pakkuja ja/v&otilde;i temaga koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutseva isiku v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise ebaseaduslikul avalikustamisel v&otilde;i selle muul viisil sihtemitendi aktsion&auml;ridele k&auml;ttesaadavaks tegemisel v&otilde;i pakkuja ja/v&otilde;i temaga koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutseva isiku poolt muude k&auml;esoleva seadusega vastuolus olevate tegude tegemisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1 (1)) The securities supervision authority has the right to issue a mandatory precept to the registrar of the Estonian Central Register of Securities for immediate execution to freeze the securities account of a tenderer and/or a person acting in concert with the tenderer for a specified term upon unlawful publication of a takeover bid, or upon making it otherwise accessible to the shareholders of the target issuer, or upon performance of other acts which are contrary to this Act by a tenderer and/or a person acting in concert with the tenderer. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ettekirjutus v&auml;ljastatakse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul osalejale v&otilde;i tema esindajale allkirja vastu vahetult v&otilde;i posti teel v&auml;ljastusteatega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Precepts are issued directly to securities market participants or representatives thereof who shall provide a signature confirming receipt or are sent by post with advice of delivery. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Tehtud ettekirjutuse vaidlustamiseks v&otilde;ib v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul osaleja p&ouml;&ouml;rduda 15 kalendrip&auml;eva jooksul ettekirjutuse tegemisest arvates kohtu poole. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In order to contest an issued precept, a securities market participant has the right of recourse to a court within fifteen calendar days after the precept is issued. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul osaleja peab p&auml;rast ettekirjutuse saamist koheselt asuma selle t&auml;itmisele, ettekirjutuse vaidlustamine kohtus ei peata selle t&auml;itmise kohustust. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A securities market participant shall, immediately after receipt of a precept, undertake the implementation thereof; contestation of a precept in court does not suspend the requirement to implement the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve ettekirjutuse mittet&auml;itmisel v&otilde;i mittekohasel t&auml;itmisel 15 kalendrip&auml;eva jooksul ettekirjutuse tegemisest arvates kohaldatakse juriidilisele isikule k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 31 s&auml;testatud vastutust ning f&uuml;&uuml;silisele isikule haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus (RT 1992, 29, 396; 1997, 66-68, 1109; 73, 1201; 81, 1361; 81, 1362; 86, 1459; 86, 1461; 87, 1466; 87, 1467; 93, 1561; 93, 1563; 93, 1564; 93, 1565; 1998, 2, 42; 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 410; 34, 484; 36/37, 552; 36/37, 553; 38, 562; 51, 756; 51, 759; 52/53, 771; 60, 951; 60, 952) s&auml;testatud vastutust. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Legal persons are liable pursuant to &sect; 31 of this Act and natural persons are liable pursuant to the Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; 1997, 66-68, 1109; 73, 1201; 81, 1361; 81, 1362; 86, 1459; 86, 1461; 87, 1466; 87, 1467; 93, 1561; 93, 1563; 93, 1564; 93, 1565; 1998, 2, 42; 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 410; 34, 484; 36/37, 552; 36/37, 553; 38, 562; 51, 756; 51, 759; 52/53, 771; 60, 951; 60, 952) for failure to implement or for inadequate implementation of a precept of the securities supervision authority within fifteen days after it is issued. </inglise>
<eesti>(03.04.96 j&otilde;ust. 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </eesti>
<inglise>(03.04.96 entered into force 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </inglise>
<eesti>V osa </eesti>
<inglise>Part V </inglise>
<eesti>Vastutus k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise eest </eesti>
<inglise>Liability for Violation of this Act or Legislation Arising Therefrom </inglise>
<eesti>(03.04.96 j&otilde;ust. 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </eesti>
<inglise>(03.04.96 entered into force 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 30. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 30. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastutus k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise eest </eesti>
<inglise>Liability for violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i selle alusel antud &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise eest vastutavad: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The following persons are liable for violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom: </inglise>
<eesti>1) f&uuml;&uuml;silised isikud - haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku alusel, kui see rikkumine ei too kaasa kriminaalvastutust; </eesti>
<inglise>1) natural persons, pursuant to the Code of Administrative Offences if the violation is not subject to criminal liability; </inglise>
<eesti>2) juriidilised isikud - k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahv 31 alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>2) legal persons, pursuant to &sect; 31 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui f&uuml;&uuml;siline isik rikub k&auml;esolevat seadust v&otilde;i sellest tulenevaid &otilde;igusakte, tegutsedes juriidilise isiku nimel v&otilde;i huvides, on &otilde;iguserikkumise eest vastutavad m&otilde;lemad ning karistust tuleb v&otilde;imalusel kohaldada nii juriidilisele kui ka f&uuml;&uuml;silisele isikule. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If a natural person acting on behalf of or in the interests of a legal person violates this Act or legislation arising therefrom, both persons are liable for the violation of law and punishment shall, if possible, be imposed on both the legal person and the natural person. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Juriidilisele isikule karistuse kohaldamisel k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise eest arvestatakse &otilde;iguserikkumise raskust ja laadi. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon imposition of punishment for violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom on legal persons, the gravity and nature of the violation of law shall be considered. </inglise>
<eesti>(03.04.96 j&otilde;ust. 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </eesti>
<inglise>(03.04.96 entered into force 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 31. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 31. </inglise>
<eesti>Juriidilise isiku haldusvastutus k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise eest </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability of legal persons for violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite avaliku v&auml;ljalaske registreerimise kohustuse, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite avaliku v&auml;ljalaske registreerimise korra, k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 11 l&otilde;ikes 3 (1) nimetatud emissiooniprospekti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele koosk&otilde;lastamiseks esitamise kohustuse, emissiooniprospektile esitatavate n&otilde;uete, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite avaliku v&auml;ljalaske v&auml;ljakuulutamise ning reklaami ja avaliku levitamise tingimuste, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite tagasiostmise kohustuse rikkumise, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele informatsiooni esitamise, t&auml;iendava aruandluse ja andmete esitamise n&otilde;ude mittet&auml;itmise eest - </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A fine in the amount of 5 000 to 300 000 kroons shall be imposed for violation of the requirement to register a public issue of securities, the procedure for registration of a public issue of securities, the requirement to submit a prospectus specified in subsection 11 (3 (1)) of this Act to the securities supervision authority for approval, the requirements for a prospectus, the conditions for announcement and advertising of a public issue or public distribution of securities, or the requirement to repurchase securities, or for failure to fulfil the requirement to submit information, additional reporting and information to the securities supervision authority. </inglise>
<eesti>m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 5 000 kuni 300 000 krooni suuruses summas. (18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. </eesti>
<inglise>(03.04.96 entered into force 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528; 18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>

<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve poolt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite esmaslevitamise peatamise n&otilde;ude rikkumise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 10 000 kuni 500 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A fine in the amount of 10 000 to 500 000 kroons shall be imposed for violation of the requirement of the securities supervision authority to suspend a primary distribution of securities. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&auml;ljalaske kohta esitatud v&otilde;i avaldatud informatsiooni &otilde;igsuse kohustuse, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite esmaslevitamisel investorite v&otilde;rdse informeerimise kohustuse, emitendi l&auml;hikondsete poolt teostatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitehingutest teatamise kohustuse ning konfidentsiaalse informatsiooni p&otilde;hjal s&otilde;lmitud tehingute keelu n&otilde;ude mittet&auml;itmise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 10 000 kuni 1 000 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A fine in the amount of 10 000 to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed for failure to fulfil the requirement of correctness of information provided or published concerning an issue of securities, the requirement to notify investors equally of a primary distribution of securities, the requirement to give notice of securities transactions effected by insiders, or for violation of the prohibition on entering into a transaction based on confidential information. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegutsemisel v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiturul ilma tegevuslitsentsita - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 500 000 kuni 1 000 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A fine in the amount of 500 000 to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed on a professional securities market participant for operating in the market without an activity licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(03.04.96 j&otilde;ust. 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </eesti>
<inglise>(03.04.96 entered into force 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) &Uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemise kohustuse rikkumise eest, kui isikule ei olnud antud n&otilde;usolekut loobuda kohustusliku &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemisest, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise v&otilde;i selle mitte&otilde;igeaegse v&otilde;i mittet&auml;ieliku t&auml;itmise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 100 000 kuni 1 000 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A fine in the amount of 100 000 to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed for violation of an obligation to make a takeover bid if the person has not been granted consent to withdraw from making a mandatory takeover bid, for failure to comply with a precept issued by the securities supervision authority or for failure to comply therewith on time or in full. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Pakkuja poolt &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise raames samaliigiliste aktsiate omanike ebav&otilde;rdse kohtlemise eest, pakkuja v&otilde;i sihtemitendi poolt sihtisikutele &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise kaalumiseks olulise, &otilde;ige, t&auml;pse, t&auml;ieliku v&otilde;i &uuml;hesuguse teabe andmata j&auml;tmise eest v&otilde;i eksitava, eba&otilde;ige v&otilde;i ebat&auml;pse teabe andmise eest v&otilde;i erinevatele sihtisikutele erisuguse teabe andmise eest, samuti sihtisikutel &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise kaalumise takistamise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 50 000 kuni 100 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A fine in the amount of 50 000 to 100 000 kroons shall be imposed on a tenderer for unequal treatment of holders of shares of the same class within a takeover bid, and on a tenderer or target issuer for failure to provide the target persons with significant, correct, accurate, complete or identical information, or for provision of misleading, incorrect or inaccurate information, or for provision of different information to different target persons for considering a takeover bid, and for hindering the target persons upon consideration of a takeover bid. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Pakkuja, juriidilisest isikust pakkuja tegevjuhtkonna liikme, juhatuse liikme, n&otilde;ukogu liikme v&otilde;i neid asendava organi liikme, sihtemitendi, selle sihtemitendi tegevjuhtkonna liikme, juhatuse liikme v&otilde;i n&otilde;ukogu liikme, eelnimetatutega koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutseva isiku v&otilde;i sihtemitendi aktsion&auml;ri poolt sihtemitendi aktsiaid noteeriva b&ouml;rsi reglemendi &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumist reguleerivate s&auml;tete rikkumise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 500 000 kuni 1 000 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) A fine in the amount of 500 000 to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed on a tenderer, members of the management, management board or supervisory board or the body substituting the management, management board or supervisory board of a tenderer who is a legal person, a target issuer, members of the management, management board or supervisory board of the target issuer, persons acting in concert with the above-mentioned persons, or a shareholder of the target issuer for violation of the provisions which regulate a takeover bid and contained in the rules of the exchange which quotes the shares of the target issuer. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Pakkuja v&otilde;i temaga koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutseva isiku poolt sellesama sihtemitendi suhtes &uuml;he aasta jooksul &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumisest uue &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemise eest, b&ouml;rsi poolt &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise reeglite kehtestamisel v&otilde;i muutmisel nende v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalvele koosk&otilde;lastamiseks esitamata j&auml;tmise eest, Eesti V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite Keskregistri pidaja poolt viivitamatuks t&auml;itmiseks antud kohustusliku ettekirjutuse - blokeerida t&auml;htajaliselt pakkuja ja/v&otilde;i temaga koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutseva isiku v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto - t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 50 000 kuni 500 000 krooni suuruses summas. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) A fine in the amount of 50 000 to 500 000 kroons shall be imposed on a tenderer or a person acting in concert with the tenderer for making a new takeover bid in respect of the same target issuer within one year after the term of the takeover bid has passed, on the exchange upon establishment or amendment of the rules for a takeover bid for failure to submit these to the securities supervision authority for approval, for failure to comply with a mandatory precept for immediate execution to freeze for a specified term the securities account of a tenderer and/or a person acting in concert with the tenderer issued by the registrar of the Estonian Central Register of Securities. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise protokolli koostamine </eesti>
<inglise>Preparation of report of administrative offence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontrollijal on &otilde;igus koostada protokoll juriidilise isiku poolt k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise kohta k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahv 31 alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Inspectors have the right to prepare a report on a violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom by legal persons, on the basis of &sect; 31 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(10.06.98 j&otilde;ust. 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979) </eesti>
<inglise>(10.06.98 entered into force 01.08.98 - RT I 1998, 61, 979) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud protokoll peab sisaldama j&auml;rgmisi andmeid: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The report specified in subsection (1) of this section shall set out the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) koostamise aeg ja koht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the date and place of preparation; </inglise>
<eesti>2) selle asutuse nimetus ja aadress, mille nimel protokoll koostatakse; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the name and address of the agency in whose name the report is prepared; </inglise>
<eesti>3) protokolli koostanud isiku ametinimetus, ees- ja perekonnanimi; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the official title, given name and surname of the person who prepared the report; </inglise>
<eesti>4) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja nimetus v&otilde;i &auml;rinimi, registreerimise number ja asukoht; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the name or business name, registration number and location of the administrative offender; </inglise>
<eesti>5) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja ees- ja perekonnanimi ning ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the given name, surname and office of the representative of the administrative offender; </inglise>
<eesti>6) haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise koht, aeg ja kirjeldus; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the place, date and description of the administrative offence; </inglise>
<eesti>7) viide k&auml;esoleva seaduse s&auml;tetele, mille alusel haldusvastutust kohaldatakse; </eesti>
<inglise>7) a reference to the provisions of this Act which are the bases for imposition of administrative liability; </inglise>
<eesti>8) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja seletus v&otilde;i m&auml;rge seletuse andmisest loobumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>8) the explanation provided by the representative of the administrative offender or a notation concerning the refusal to provide an explanation. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Protokollile kirjutavad alla selle koostanud isik ja haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A report shall be signed by the person who prepared the report and the representative of the administrative offender. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja keeldub protokollile alla kirjutamast, tehakse sellesse vastav kanne. </eesti>
<inglise>If the representative of the administrative offender refuses to sign the report, a corresponding entry shall be made therein. </inglise>
<eesti>Protokollile lisatakse haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja kirjalikud m&auml;rkused protokolli, samuti protokollile allakirjutamisest keeldumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>Written notations of the representative of the administrative offender concerning the report and on the refusal to sign the report shall be appended to the report. </inglise>
<eesti>(03.04.96 j&otilde;ust. 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </eesti>
<inglise>(03.04.96 entered into force 03.05.96 - RT I 1996, 26, 528) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 33. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 33. </inglise>
<eesti>Menetlus juriidilise isiku haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise asjas </eesti>
<inglise>Procedure in matters of administrative offence committed by legal persons </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Menetluse kord, sealhulgas sanktsioonide rakendamine ja nende vaidlustamine k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise asjas juriidilise isiku poolt, toimub haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku menetluskorda j&auml;rgides. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The procedure, including the enforcement of sanctions and contestation thereof, in matters of violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom by legal persons is effected pursuant to the procedure of the Code of Administrative Offences. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise asja arutamise ja karistuse m&auml;&auml;ramise &otilde;igus on halduskohtunikul ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve juhil. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An administrative court judge and the director of the securities supervision authority have the right to hear and impose punishment for matters of violation of this Act or legislation arising therefrom. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalve juhil on &otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;rata rahatrahvi kuni 50 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>The director of the securities supervision authority has the right to impose a fine of up to 50 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.01.2000 j&otilde;ust. 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.01.2000 entered into force 25.02.2000 - RT I 2000, 10, 55) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel juriidilisele isikule m&auml;&auml;ratud rahatrahv n&otilde;utakse sisse haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus ja t&auml;itemenetluse seadustikus (RT I 1993, 49, 693; RT I 1997, 43/44, 723; 1998, 41/42, 625; 51, 756) kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Fines imposed on legal persons pursuant to this Act shall be collected pursuant to the procedure established by the Code of Administrative Offences and the Code of Enforcement Procedure (RT I 1993, 49, 693; RT I 1997, 43/44, 723; 1998, 41/42, 625; 51, 756). </inglise>
